{
  "id": "nn_mpr5pgri_kcvh9wsdg",
  "title": "Array (basics) Largestt",
  "content": "<div><br></div><div>\n\n<h1 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"dsa\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"0\">DSA</h1><h1 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-phase-1--array-basics--largest-element\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"2\">📌 PHASE 1 — ARRAY BASICS &amp; LARGEST ELEMENT</h1><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"4\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-what-is-array-ds\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"6\">🔹 What is Array (DS)?</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"8\">Array is a&nbsp;<strong>DS (Data Structure)</strong>&nbsp;which store&nbsp;<strong>similar element</strong>.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"10\">Agar yeh DS ek particular type ka hai</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"12\">toh&nbsp;<strong>similar type hona chahiye</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"14\">chahe&nbsp;<strong>integer ho, char ho, string ho, pair ho</strong>.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"16\">Array looks like</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-css\" data-line=\"18\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[ ]</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[ ]</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[ ]</span>\n\n</code></pre></div><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"23\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-declaration-of-array\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"25\">🔹 Declaration of Array</h2><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"in-c--c\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"27\">In C / C++</h3><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"29\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> arr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>];\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"in-java\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"34\">In Java</h3><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">java</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-java hljs\" data-line=\"36\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> arr[] =newarr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>];\n\n</code></pre></div><blockquote style=\"background-color:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(36, 37, 38);color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"41\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"41\">jab aap yeh likh dete ho toh kya hota hai ki</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"44\"><strong>size 6 ka array create hota hai</strong></p></blockquote><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"46\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"46\">agar&nbsp;<strong>inside main</strong>&nbsp;declare kiya →&nbsp;<strong>garbage values</strong>&nbsp;aati hain</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"47\">agar&nbsp;<strong>global</strong>&nbsp;declare kiya →&nbsp;<strong>0 se filled hota hai</strong>&nbsp;(C++)</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"49\">Java me bhi default value&nbsp;<strong>0 hoti hai</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"51\">Python ka sure nahi 😅</p><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-note-correction\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"53\">📝 NOTE (Correction)</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"55\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"55\">Java me bhi&nbsp;<strong>garbage values nahi hoti</strong>, default value&nbsp;<strong>0 hoti hai</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"56\">Python me traditional array nahi hota, list hoti hai (dynamic)</li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"58\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-maximum-size-of-array\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"60\">🔹 Maximum Size of Array</h2><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"62\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"62\"><strong>Inside&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">int main()</code></strong>&nbsp;→&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">10^6</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"63\"><strong>Global array</strong>&nbsp;→&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">10^7</code></li></ul><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-note-correction-1\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"65\">📝 NOTE (Correction)</h3><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"67\">Yeh&nbsp;<strong>stack vs heap limitation</strong>&nbsp;ki wajah se hota hai.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"69\">Global arrays heap/static memory me jaate hain.</p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"71\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-accessing-an-array\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"73\">🔹 Accessing an Array</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"75\">Array ko access karne ke liye&nbsp;<strong>index</strong>&nbsp;use hota hai.</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"77\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"77\">index starts from&nbsp;<strong>0 to n-1</strong></li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"79\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">print</span>(arr[i]);\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"86\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-where-is-array-stored-in-memory\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"88\">🔹 Where is Array Stored in Memory?</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"90\">Array&nbsp;<strong>computer memory</strong>&nbsp;me store hota hai.</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"92\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"92\">maan lo array ka&nbsp;<strong>first block random x location</strong>&nbsp;pe hai</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"93\">hume x pata hota hai</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"94\">0th index → x</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"95\">1st index → x + 1</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"96\">2nd index → x + 2</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"98\">Array&nbsp;<strong>continuous memory</strong>&nbsp;me store hota hai.</p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"100\"><h1 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-largest-element-in-an-array\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"102\">🔥 LARGEST ELEMENT IN AN ARRAY</h1><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"104\">Hum&nbsp;<strong>direct solution nahi denge</strong>,</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"106\">interview ko&nbsp;<strong>drive karna hai</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"108\">Flow hoga:</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"110\">👉&nbsp;<strong>Brute → Better → Optimal</strong></p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"112\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"example\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"114\">Example</h2><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"116\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">arr[] = [3, 2, 1, 5, 2]\n\n</code></pre></div><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"121\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-brute-force-approach\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"123\">🔹 Brute Force Approach</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"125\">Idea:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"127\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"127\"><strong>Array ko sort karo</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"128\"><strong>Last element pick karo</strong></li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"130\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">largest = arr[n<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>];\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"135\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"137\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"137\">Sorting →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n log n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"138\">Space →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(1)</code>&nbsp;(kuch naya nahi bana rahe)</li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"140\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-optimal-approach\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"142\">🔹 Optimal Approach</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"144\">Idea:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"146\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"146\">First element ko&nbsp;<strong>largest maan lo</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"147\">Traverse karo</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"148\">Agar koi bada mil jaye → largest update</li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"150\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">largest = arr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &gt; largest) {\n        largest = arr[i];\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">print</span>(largest);\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity-1\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"163\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"165\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"165\"><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"166\">Optimise ho gaya 🎯</li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"168\"><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"170\">👉&nbsp;<strong>Next Phase me cover karenge:</strong></p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"172\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"172\">Second Largest</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"173\">Second Smallest</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"174\">Check if array sorted</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"175\">Remove duplicates (Brute → Optimal)</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"177\">Bolo&nbsp;<strong>Phase 2 chalu karein? 💪</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"179\">next</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"181\">Perfect 👍</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"183\">👉&nbsp;<strong>PHASE 2: Second Largest, Second Smallest, Check Sorted Array</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"185\">(Again reminder:&nbsp;<strong>aapke words, language, flow same rakhe gaye hain</strong>, bas structure + spelling + syntax clean kiya hai.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"187\">Galat cheez ke niche&nbsp;<strong>NOTE</strong>&nbsp;diya hai.)</p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"189\"><h1 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-phase-2--second-largest--second-smallest--check-sorted\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"191\">📌 PHASE 2 — SECOND LARGEST / SECOND SMALLEST / CHECK SORTED</h1><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"193\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-second-largest-element-in-array\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"195\">🔥 SECOND LARGEST ELEMENT IN ARRAY</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"197\">Interview me&nbsp;<strong>second largest</strong>&nbsp;ya&nbsp;<strong>second smallest</strong>&nbsp;dono puch sakte hain.</p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"199\"><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-brute-force-approach-1\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"201\">🔹 Brute Force Approach</h3><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"203\">Idea:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"205\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"205\">Array ko&nbsp;<strong>sort</strong>&nbsp;kar do</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"206\"><code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">arr[n-2]</code>&nbsp;output hoga</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"208\">Par dikkat yeh hai 👇</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"210\">kya pata&nbsp;<strong>saare element same ho</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"212\">ya last ke&nbsp;<strong>4–5 same ho</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"214\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"216\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">1 2 4 5 7 7\n\n</code></pre></div><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"221\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"221\"><code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">largest = arr[n-1]</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"222\"><code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">n-1</code>&nbsp;se peeche traverse karo</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"223\">jo&nbsp;<strong>largest ke barabar nahi ho</strong>&nbsp;→ wahi second largest</li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"225\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">largest = arr[n<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>];\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i = n<span class=\"hljs-number\">-2</span>; i &gt;=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i--) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] != largest) {\n        secondLargest = arr[i];\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// necessary kyuki aage ka koi fayda nahi</span>\n    }\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"worst-case\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"237\">Worst Case</h3><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"239\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">1 7 7 7 7 7\n\n</code></pre></div><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"244\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"244\">poora traverse karna padega</li></ul><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity-2\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"246\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"248\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"248\">Sorting →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n log n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"249\">Loop →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"250\">Total →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n log n + n)</code></li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"252\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-better-approach-2-pass\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"254\">🔹 Better Approach (2 Pass)</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"256\">Idea:</p><ol style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"258\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"258\"><strong>First pass</strong>&nbsp;→ largest nikaalo</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"259\"><strong>Second pass</strong>&nbsp;→ second largest nikaalo</li></ol><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"261\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"263\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">1 2 4 7 7 5\n\n</code></pre></div><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"268\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"268\">largest = 7</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"269\">secondLargest = -1 (maan liya array me positives hain)</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"271\">Condition:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"273\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"273\">element&nbsp;<strong>largest se chota ho</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"274\">element&nbsp;<strong>secondLargest se bada ho</strong></li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"276\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">largest = arr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// First pass</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &gt; largest) {\n        largest = arr[i];\n    }\n}\n\nsecondLargest =<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Second pass</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &gt; secondLargest &amp;&amp; arr[i] != largest) {\n        secondLargest = arr[i];\n    }\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity-3\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"297\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"299\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"299\">First pass →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"300\">Second pass →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"301\">Total →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(2n)</code>&nbsp;≈&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"303\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-optimal-approach-single-pass\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"305\">🔹 Optimal Approach (Single Pass)</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"307\">Idea:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"309\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"309\"><strong>largest</strong>&nbsp;aur&nbsp;<strong>secondLargest</strong>&nbsp;dono saath manage karo</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"311\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"313\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">1, 2, 4, 7, 7, 5\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"318\">Steps:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"320\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"320\">first element → largest</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"321\">secondLargest ko&nbsp;<strong>bahut chota</strong>&nbsp;maan lo</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"323\">Logic:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"325\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"325\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"325\">agar koi element&nbsp;<strong>largest se bada</strong>&nbsp;ho</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"327\">→ secondLargest = largest</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"329\">→ largest = current element</p></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"331\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"331\">agar element&nbsp;<strong>largest se chota</strong>&nbsp;ho</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"333\">aur&nbsp;<strong>secondLargest se bada</strong>&nbsp;ho</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"335\">→ secondLargest update</p></li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"338\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">largest = arr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\nslargest =<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>;<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// agar negative values ho sakti hain toh INT_MIN</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &gt; largest) {\n        slargest = largest;\n        largest = arr[i];\n    }\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">elseif</span>(arr[i] &lt; largest &amp;&amp; arr[i] &gt; slargest) {\n        slargest = arr[i];\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> slargest;\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"356\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"358\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">8 7 5 6 7 8 9\n\n</code></pre></div><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"363\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-second-smallest-element\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"365\">🔥 SECOND SMALLEST ELEMENT</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"367\">Same logic bas&nbsp;<strong>ulta</strong>.</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"369\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"369\">smallest = first element</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"370\">ssmallest =&nbsp;<strong>INT_MAX</strong></li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"372\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">smallest = arr[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\nssmallest = INT_MAX;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &lt; smallest) {\n        ssmallest = smallest;\n        smallest = arr[i];\n    }\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">elseif</span>(arr[i] &gt; smallest &amp;&amp; arr[i] &lt; ssmallest) {\n        ssmallest = arr[i];\n    }\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity-4\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"388\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"390\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"390\"><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"391\"><strong>Single pass</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"392\">Better than better solution 😎</li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"394\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-check-if-array-is-sorted\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"396\">🔍 CHECK IF ARRAY IS SORTED</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"398\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-csharp\" data-line=\"400\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">[<span class=\"hljs-meta\">1, 2, 3, 3, 4</span>] → sorted\n[<span class=\"hljs-meta\">1, 2, 1, 3, 4</span>] →<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">not</span> sorted\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"406\">Isme&nbsp;<strong>brute / better / optimal</strong>&nbsp;ki koi zarurat nahi</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"408\">Simple logic hai.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"410\">Idea:</p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"412\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"412\">har element ko&nbsp;<strong>previous se compare</strong>&nbsp;karo</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"413\">agar kahin bhi chota mil gaya → not sorted</li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"415\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[i] &gt;= arr[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>]) {\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// kuch nahi karo</span>\n    }\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\nreturnfalse;\n    }\n}\n\nreturntrue;\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"explanation\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"429\">Explanation</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"431\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"431\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"431\">agar loop poora chal gaya</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"433\">matlab&nbsp;<strong>koi dikkat nahi aayi</strong></p></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"435\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"435\">isliye last me&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">return true</code></p></li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"437\"><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"439\">👉&nbsp;<strong>Next Phase me aayega:</strong></p><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"441\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"441\">Remove duplicates from sorted array</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"442\">Brute → Optimal (Two Pointer)</li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"444\"><h1 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-phase-3--remove-duplicates-in-place\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"446\">📌 PHASE 3 — REMOVE DUPLICATES (IN-PLACE)</h1><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"448\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-problem-statement\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"450\">🔥 Problem Statement</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"452\">Sorted array diya hai,&nbsp;<strong>duplicates remove karne hain in-place</strong>.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"454\">Example:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-ini\" data-line=\"456\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">arr</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>]\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"461\">Output:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-ini\" data-line=\"463\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">arr</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, _, _, _, _]\n\n</code></pre></div><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"468\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"468\">first&nbsp;<strong>unique elements starting me aane chahiye</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"469\">baaki jagah&nbsp;<strong>kuch bhi ho sakta hai</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"470\"><strong>new array nahi banana</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"471\">same array use karna hai</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"473\">Agar&nbsp;<strong>3 unique elements hain</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"475\">toh&nbsp;<strong>starting ke 3 index</strong>&nbsp;pe hi hone chahiye.</p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"477\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-brute-force-approach-2\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"479\">🔹 Brute Force Approach</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"481\">Idea:</p><blockquote style=\"background-color:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(36, 37, 38);color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"483\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"483\">“unique chahiye mujhe”</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"486\">mere dimag me&nbsp;<strong>set</strong>&nbsp;aa raha hai</p></blockquote><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"488\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"488\">set duplicate allow nahi karta</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"489\">array traverse karo</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"490\">set me insert karo</li></ul><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"492\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">set&lt;<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span>&gt; st;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {\n    st.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">insert</span>(arr[i]);\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"501\">Ab set me&nbsp;<strong>sirf unique elements</strong>&nbsp;hain.</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"503\">Ab wapas array me daalna hai 👇</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"505\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> index =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">auto</span> it : st) {\n    arr[index] = it;\n    index++;\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"complexity-5\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"514\">Complexity</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"516\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"516\">set insertion →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n log n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"517\">array overwrite →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"518\">total →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n log n + n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"519\">space →&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code>&nbsp;(extra set use hua)</li></ul><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-note\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"521\">📝 NOTE</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"523\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"523\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"523\">Problem ne bola tha&nbsp;<strong>in-place</strong>,</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"525\">lekin yahan&nbsp;<strong>extra space</strong>&nbsp;use ho rahi hai</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"527\">isliye interview me yeh&nbsp;<strong>optimal nahi maana jaata</strong></p></li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"530\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-optimal-approach-two-pointer\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"532\">🔹 Optimal Approach (Two Pointer)</h2><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"534\">Yeh&nbsp;<strong>important interview solution</strong>&nbsp;hai 🔥</p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"536\">Given:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-ini\" data-line=\"538\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">arr</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>]\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"idea-aapke-words-me\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"543\">Idea (aapke words me):</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"545\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"545\">array&nbsp;<strong>sorted hai</strong>&nbsp;(bahut important)</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"546\">ek pointer hoga jo&nbsp;<strong>unique element ko point karega</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"547\">dusra pointer aage jaa ke&nbsp;<strong>naya element dhundega</strong></li></ul><blockquote style=\"background-color:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(36, 37, 38);color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"549\"><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"549\">jo first pointer hai</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"552\">wo initially&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">arr[0]</code>&nbsp;pe hoga</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"554\">aur wo dhundega ki</p><p dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"556\">“mere jaisa element kaha nahi mil raha”</p></blockquote><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"559\">Jaha&nbsp;<strong>different element milega</strong></p><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"561\">waha usko&nbsp;<strong>next position pe daal denge</strong></p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"563\"><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"two-pointer-explanation\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"565\">Two Pointer Explanation</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"567\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"567\"><code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">i</code>&nbsp;→ unique element ka index</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"568\"><code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">j</code>&nbsp;→ traversal ke liye</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"570\">Start:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-ini\" data-line=\"572\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">i</span> =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"577\">Loop:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span class=\"code-lang-label\">cpp</span><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line language-cpp hljs\" data-line=\"579\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> j =<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; j &lt; n; j++) {\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(arr[j] != arr[i]) {\n        i++;\n        arr[i] = arr[j];\n    }\n}\n\n</code></pre></div><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"final-result\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"589\">Final Result</h3><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"591\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"591\">array ke&nbsp;<strong>0 se i tak</strong>&nbsp;→ unique elements</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"592\">total unique elements =&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">i + 1</code></li></ul><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"594\"><h3 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"example-dry-run\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"596\">Example Dry Run</h3><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-ini\" data-line=\"598\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">arr</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>]\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">i</span> =<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n</code></pre></div><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"604\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"604\">j=1 → same (1==1) → ignore</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"605\">j=2 → different (2!=1) → i=1 → arr[1]=2</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"606\">j=3 → same → ignore</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"607\">j=4 → same → ignore</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"608\">j=5 → different → i=2 → arr[2]=3</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"609\">j=6 → same → ignore</li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"611\">Final array:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-csharp\" data-line=\"613\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">[<span class=\"hljs-meta\">1, 2, 3, x, x, x, x</span>]\n\n</code></pre></div><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"618\">Unique count:</p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre style=\"background-color:rgb(36, 37, 38)\"><code style=\"background-color:none;color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line hljs language-undefined\" data-line=\"620\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">i +1 =3\n\n</code></pre></div><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"625\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-complexity-optimal\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"627\">🔹 Complexity (Optimal)</h2><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"629\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"629\"><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(n)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"630\"><strong>Space:</strong>&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color:rgb(38, 38, 38)\">O(1)</code></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"631\"><strong>Single pass</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"632\">Fully&nbsp;<strong>in-place</strong></li></ul><p style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"634\">🔥 This is the&nbsp;<strong>best solution</strong></p><hr dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"636\"><h2 style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" id=\"-summary-interview-friendly\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"638\">✅ Summary (Interview Friendly)</h2><ul style=\"color:rgb(187, 190, 191)\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"640\"><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"640\">Sorted array hai →&nbsp;<strong>Two Pointer</strong></li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line\" data-line=\"641\">Extra space allowed → set</li><li dir=\"auto\" class=\"code-line code-active-line\" data-line=\"642\">In-place chahiye →&nbsp;<strong>optimal solution use karo</strong></li></ul>\n\n<br></div>",
